  <h2>Our Exterior Painting Process</h2>
  
  <h3>Surface Preparation & Protection</h3>
  <p>
    We meticulously prepare all surfaces with power washing, scraping, and sanding, followed by priming to ensure long-lasting results. Our preparation process includes:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Thorough cleaning to remove dirt, mildew, and loose paint</li>
    <li>Careful scraping and sanding of degraded areas</li>
    <li>Specialized dustless sanding technology for cleaner, healthier work environments</li>
    <li>Premium primers applied to bare wood and problem areas</li>
    <li>Caulking of gaps and seams to prevent moisture intrusion</li>
  </ul>

